content.subtitle: Stop waiting for legacy NAS. QuickStor deploys enterprise-grade ZFS mirroring and RAID-Z3 on bare-metal hardware.

content.title: DOMINATE THE BENCHMARKS

features.title: Self-Healing Data
features.description: Every block is checksummed. If ZFS detects silent data corruption ("bit rot"), it automatically repairs the damaged data from parity before you even know it happened.

features.title: Open Hardware
features.description: No proprietary RAID cards. No vendor lock-in. If a controller fails, plug your drives into any standard HBA and your data is accessible instantly.

features.title: Intelligent Tiering
features.description: Hybrid Storage Pools automatically route hot data to NVMe/SSD and cold data to high-capacity HDDs, giving you flash speed at spinning-disk prices.

customSections.prompt:
Create a responsive section divided into two equal horizontal halves.

Left half:

Contains exactly two text elements only:

A Title text field

A Details (body) text field

No buttons, inputs, icons, or additional text elements should be included.

Right half:

Displays a single circular (fully rounded) image.

The image must be clipped to a circular frame using proper masking (e.g., border-radius: 50% or equivalent).

If the source image exceeds the frame size, it must be cropped/clipped without distortion.

The circular frames diameter must not exceed 50% of the sections width or 100% of the sections height, whichever is smaller.

The circular image must be horizontally and vertically centered within the right half of the section.

The layout must remain visually balanced and responsive across screen sizes.
